title: Sweet Strawberry
description:
Indulge in the delightful aroma of sun-ripened strawberries gathered at the peak of summer.
This fragrance fills your space with a sugary, fruity warmth that feels like a bright afternoon in the garden.

title: Mint Candleaf
description:
Experience a revitalizing blend of garden-fresh mint infused with a hint of warm kitchen spices.
This candle creates a crisp, cooling atmosphere that perfectly balances energy with relaxation.
Wax: Top grade Soy wax that delivers a smoke less,  consistent burn
Fragrance: Premium quality ingredients with natural essential oils 
Burning Time: 70-75 hours
Dimension: 10cm x 5cm 
Weight: 400g

title: Cool Blueberries
description:
Surround yourself with the sweet and slightly tart scent of freshly picked wild blueberries.
Its refreshing berry notes provide a calming, natural breeze that transforms any room into a peaceful retreat.

title: Juicy Lemon
description:
Brighten your day with the zesty, uplifting fragrance of sliced Mediterranean lemons.
This vibrant scent cuts through the air to deliver a clean, citrusy burst of pure sunshine.

title: Fresh Orange
description:
Savor the mouth-watering scent of juicy oranges peeled straight from the citrus grove.
The rich, tangy notes provide a cheerful ambiance that is both comforting and incredibly refreshing.

title: Fragrant Cinnamon
description:
Wrap your home in the cozy, nostalgic aroma of warm cinnamon sticks and gentle spice.
This inviting scent creates a snug atmosphere, making it the perfect companion for a quiet evening indoors.

title: Summer Cherries
description:
Enjoy the bold and playful fragrance of dark, succulent cherries ripening under the July sun.
This deep fruity scent adds a touch of sweetness and charm to your living space.

title: Clean Lavender
description:
Unwind with the timeless, soothing scent of blooming lavender fields and soft floral undertones.
Designed for tranquility, this fragrance helps clear the mind and promotes a sense of deep serenity.
